description: AMUNDI MSCI EUROPE GROWTH UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI Europe Growth strategy Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to easily follow the leading stocks in European countries, growth stock representatives, with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
